introduction: Jack Hawkins is an actor from Adelaide, South Australia. Jack found his love for performing and acting when he fell in love with the idea of making an audience feel something merely through acting. Performing with the voice has always showed interest with Jack, whether it's through video games, animation, audio books, or any other form of media on the internet. Jack also has a talent for writing, designing, and editing for projects.
